...none of us will ever get to play the violin again.

507
00:35:16,590 --> 00:35:18,520
好的,谢谢你们听我说话
Well, I thank you for your attention.

508
00:35:24,130 --> 00:35:25,720
好了
All right.

509
00:35:25,900 --> 00:35:28,030
你觉得呢,中士？
What do you think, sergeant?

510
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:32,240
我觉得他们会把你活埋在法国,少校
I think they're gonna bury you in France, major.

511
00:35:32,410 --> 00:35:34,670
他们全都这样想
They think the same thing.

512
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:12,880
都下车,快
Everybody out. Move it.

513
00:36:13,050 --> 00:36:14,640
大家快点,快下车
Let's go, let's go. Move it, guys.

514
00:36:14,810 --> 00:36:17,080
听从少校指挥
You heard the major.

515
00:36:19,890 --> 00:36:22,860
- 搞什么鬼？ - 这里不是跳伞学校
- What the hell is this?   - Don't look like a jump school to me.

516
00:36:23,020 --> 00:36:24,650
不,好像是个港口
No, this is some kind of port.

517
00:36:24,820 --> 00:36:26,160
也许是南安普顿
Southampton maybe.

518
00:36:26,330 --> 00:36:28,120
或许我们能在这大干一场
Maybe we're gonna get our shots here.

519
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:32,930
快看哪
Look at that.

520
00:36:33,130 --> 00:36:34,960
真不赖啊
Oh, that's nice.

521
00:36:35,470 --> 00:36:37,870
嗨,中士,她有妹妹吗？
Hey, sarge, she got a sister?

522
00:36:38,700 --> 00:36:40,830
好了,进去吧,快点
All right, inside. Move.

523
00:36:41,610 --> 00:36:42,840
快点
Move it.

524
00:36:44,080 --> 00:36:46,810
- 来吧,老波  - 别叫我老波
- Come on, move it, Pops.   - Don't call me Pops.

525
00:36:46,980 --> 00:36:49,710
老波,别发火
Now, Pops, don't get overexcited.

526
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:52,180
他们来了
Well, here they are.

527
00:36:52,350 --> 00:36:53,580
一群帅小伙
Good-looking men.

528
00:36:53,750 --> 00:36:56,520
大洋彼岸的致命诱惑！
It's a transatlantic invasion!

529
00:36:58,060 --> 00:37:00,220
- 你好,宝贝  - 她真是美艳绝伦
- Hello, dear.   - She's gotta be dreaming.

530
00:37:00,390 --> 00:37:03,360
- 过来,坐我旁边  - 我好像是上了天堂
- Come here, sit next to me.   - Think I died and went to heaven.

531
00:37:06,330 --> 00:37:08,820
我要那个魁梧的大个子
I'll have the big tall fellow.

532
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:10,490
真贪心
Greedy.

533
00:37:11,500 --> 00:37:14,470
好了,这是玛莎
All right, this is Martha.

534
00:37:14,640 --> 00:37:17,230
玛莎是这些漂亮女孩的..
Martha's the head mistress of this...

535
00:37:17,410 --> 00:37:18,970
...妈妈桑
...very exclusive girl school.

536
00:37:29,220 --> 00:37:32,120
玛莎说你们跟突击队一样...
Martha says you're part of a very elite unit...

537
00:37:32,290 --> 00:37:34,020
...都是精英战士
...just like our commandos.

538
00:37:34,190 --> 00:37:36,290
是的,没错
Yeah. That's us.

539
00:37:36,460 --> 00:37:38,400
我们是精英战士
An elite unit.

540
00:37:38,560 --> 00:37:40,400
万里挑一的
One in a million.

541
00:37:47,310 --> 00:37:49,770
我喜欢慢舞曲
I like the slow dance numbers.

542
00:37:49,940 --> 00:37:53,710
我喜欢快点的,但晚会是为你们开的
I prefer the fast ones, Yank, but it's your party.

543
00:38:04,260 --> 00:38:07,350
噢,别着急,美国大兵,我是你的了
Wu,Easy does it, Yank, I'm on your side.

544
00:38:10,600 --> 00:38:13,060
他是个强奸犯,杀死过一个陆军妇女队成员
He's a rapist and he murdered a WAC.

545
00:38:14,070 --> 00:38:17,470
- 他应该在这里吗？ - 你们都该在这里
- You think he belongs here?   - You all belong here.

546
00:38:17,900 --> 00:38:19,800
帮我个忙
But do me a favor.

547
00:38:20,410 --> 00:38:22,640
帮我盯着他
Keep an eye on him anyway.

548
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:25,470
没问题
Consider it done.

549
00:38:27,080 --> 00:38:29,880
- 有香烟吗？ - 有,我还有口香糖
- Got any cigs?   - Yeah, chewing gum too.

550
00:38:35,690 --> 00:38:39,320
终于找到他们喜欢做的事情了
Finally found something they like to do.

551
00:38:39,490 --> 00:38:42,720
若是让高层知道了怎么办,少校？
What do you think will happen when the brass finds out, major?

552
00:38:42,900 --> 00:38:44,950
我才不管他们
Forget about the brass.

553
00:38:45,130 --> 00:38:46,860
这些人都要去送死了
I'm getting these guys killed.

554
00:38:47,030 --> 00:38:49,000
至少我该让他们...
The least I can do...

555
00:38:49,170 --> 00:38:51,400
...沾上点好运
...is let them get lucky.

556
00:40:30,270 --> 00:40:33,570
法国海岸涨潮了
The sea is full On the French coast

557
00:40:34,410 --> 00:40:37,310
月光摇曳,瞬息即灭
The light Gleams and is gone

558
00:40:38,210 --> 00:40:41,410
欢饮来到法国,我是玛丽.维兰尼
Welcome to France. I am Marie Verlaine.

559
00:40:41,580 --> 00:40:43,310
我是莱特少校
I'm Major Wright.

560
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:45,420
我们继续行军吧
Maybe we ought to keep moving.

561
00:41:02,740 --> 00:41:04,400
这边
This way.

562
00:41:13,310 --> 00:41:14,750
你父亲的事我很遗憾
I'm sorry about your father.

563
00:41:14,910 --> 00:41:17,010
- 他是被出卖的？ - 是的
- Was he betrayed?   - Of course.

564
00:41:17,180 --> 00:41:19,210
之后我就没回过家
I haven't been home since.

565
00:41:19,390 --> 00:41:23,290
进攻修道院前我们就呆在一个安全的农场
But there's a farm where we'll be safe until we hit the monastery.

566
00:41:23,460 --> 00:41:25,190
你跟那些科学家联系上了？
You been in touch with the scientists?

567
00:41:25,360 --> 00:41:28,450
项目主管,乔治.弗莱蒙等着见你们...
The project director, George Flamands, is waiting to see you...

568
00:41:28,630 --> 00:41:30,720
...不过我的先跟你说一下
...but there's something you should know.

569
00:41:30,900 --> 00:41:33,990
两周前,纳粹司令官克雷格上校觉得...
Two weeks ago, the SS Commandant Colonel Krieger...

570
00:41:34,170 --> 00:41:38,230
...那些科学家需要一点动力...
...decided the scientists at the abbey needed better motivation...

571
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:39,630
...才能把工作做好
...for their work.

572
00:41:39,810 --> 00:41:42,900
- 什么意思？ - 其中三个科学家都已结婚
- What are you talking about?   - Three of the scientists are married.

573
00:41:43,080 --> 00:41:44,870
纳粹把他们的妻子接来了
He rounded up their wives.

574
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:46,600
她们不是被关在集中营吗？
Are they in a concentration camp?

575
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:49,410
正相反,她们就在修道院里...
On the contrary, they are at the monastery.

576
00:41:49,580 --> 00:41:51,950
是第三帝国“尊贵的客人”
The "honored guests" of the Third Reich.

577
00:41:52,120 --> 00:41:54,050
我不能把他们妻子接走
I didn't come to pick up husbands and wives.

578
00:41:54,220 --> 00:41:56,520
我知道你的任务,少校
I know why you're here, major.

579
00:41:56,690 --> 00:41:59,950
你是来炸毁修道院,消灭那里的德军
To blow up the monastery and kill the Germans working there.

580
00:42:00,130 --> 00:42:02,420
我赞同你们的任务
I approve of that motive.

581
00:42:20,980 --> 00:42:23,640
我们为何不能走陆路到农场？
Why can't we stay on the land until we reach this farm?

582
00:42:23,820 --> 00:42:26,910
克雷格在每个岗哨都增加了一倍的兵力...
Krieger has doubled the security at every checkpoint...

583
00:42:27,090 --> 00:42:30,020
...将常规军编入了纳粹党卫军
...adding regular troops to the SS.

584
00:42:30,190 --> 00:42:32,820
德军一直都控制着水路...
The Germans are so used to controlling the river...

585
00:42:32,990 --> 00:42:34,930
...所以他们在此比较大意
...that they've gotten careless.

586
00:42:35,090 --> 00:42:38,090
好了,玛丽,我们上吧
All right, Marie. Let's go for it.

587
00:43:08,290 --> 00:43:11,130
好了,你们去把无线电发报机给拿下了
All right, I'm counting on you to take out the radio.

588
00:43:54,510 --> 00:43:55,970
趴下！
Get down!

589
00:45:19,060 --> 00:45:20,920
斯图文特去哪了？
Where's Sturdivant?

590
00:45:22,130 --> 00:45:23,620
他死了
He's dead.

591
00:45:25,460 --> 00:45:27,460
史坦,去发报机那里
Stern, get on the radio.

592
00:45:27,630 --> 00:45:30,120
熟悉一下此船的代号...
Familiarize yourself with the vessel's call letters...

593
00:45:30,300 --> 00:45:32,290
...但不要发送无线电信号
...but don't attempt any transmission.

594
00:45:32,470 --> 00:45:34,500
明白
You got it.

595
00:45:35,570 --> 00:45:37,570
我们清理一下船只
Let's get this craft cleaned up.

596
00:45:37,740 --> 00:45:41,010
坐一等舱,把船开到河口
We're going up the estuary. First class.

597
00:45:41,180 --> 00:45:43,050
然后与抵抗组织联系
And make contact with the Resistance.

598
00:45:55,090 --> 00:45:57,430
- 晚上好,玛丽  - 晚上好,弗朗索瓦
- Good evening, Marie.   - Good evening, Francois.

599
00:45:57,600 --> 00:45:59,760
他们到了,我们接上了
They are here now. We made it.

600
00:45:59,930 --> 00:46:02,090
- 太好了  - 是
- Very good.   - Yes.

601
00:46:28,330 --> 00:46:31,760
嗨,这里就像我离开的那个家
Hey, this is just like home. The one I ran away from.

602
00:46:31,930 --> 00:46:35,760
少校,为何不能喝这些法国美酒？
Major, how come we can't drink some of this fine French wine?

603
00:46:35,930 --> 00:46:39,030
因为我不想有群醉鬼手下
Because I don't want a dozen winos on my hands, that's why.

604
00:46:39,200 --> 00:46:41,140
都听好了
Now listen.

605
00:46:41,370 --> 00:46:44,600
你们一直在这里呆到晚上九点半
You're all gonna stay down here until 21：30 hours.

606
00:46:44,780 --> 00:46:47,110
抵抗组织会为你们放哨...
The Resistance people are gonna post guards...

607
00:46:47,280 --> 00:46:51,080
- ..你们都呆在这里  - 那些法国姑娘呢,少校？
- ... but you all stay out of sight.   - Where are the French girls, major?

608
00:46:51,250 --> 00:46:54,240
- 她们在英国把我们服伺的不错  - 是呀
- They did us a fine job in England.   - Yeah.

609
00:46:55,020 --> 00:46:58,220
我只想让你们知道在为何而战
Well, I just wanted you to know what you were fighting for.

610
00:46:58,490 --> 00:47:00,820
- 方提纳！ - 少校？
- Fontenac!   - Major?

611
00:47:01,460 --> 00:47:03,430
我们待会去修道院
We're going to the monastery.

612
00:47:03,700 --> 00:47:06,390
玛丽安排我们跟项目主管见面
Marie's arranged a meeting with the director of the project.

613
00:47:06,570 --> 00:47:08,620
乔治.弗莱蒙
George Flamands.

614
00:47:29,220 --> 00:47:31,050
- 怎么了？ - 不知道,上校
- What happened?   - We're not sure, colonel.

615
00:47:31,220 --> 00:47:34,160
这条船昨天下午5点在SSM地区...
The boat was last in communication at Salles-sur-Mer...

616
00:47:34,360 --> 00:47:36,850
...跟我们失去了联系
...about 5 p. m. yesterday evening.

617
00:47:37,030 --> 00:47:41,300
我们派它去巡视河口和水路,一直到晚上7点
It was to patrol the estuary and the approaches until 1900 hours.

618
00:47:41,470 --> 00:47:45,200
2分钟前我们在河口发现了船,但上面空无一人
It was found with no signs of life at the estuary about 20 minutes ago.

619
00:47:45,370 --> 00:47:46,800
- 船员呢？ - 都不见了
- What about the crew?   - Gone.

620
00:47:46,970 --> 00:47:50,370
前后甲板上都布满弹孔
There are many bullet holes on the forward and afterdecks.

621
00:47:50,540 --> 00:47:52,480
通知第七军总部
Notify Army Group 7 headquarters.

622
00:47:52,640 --> 00:47:55,940
是,长官。说是突击队袭击吗,上校？
Yes, sir. A commando attack, colonel?

623
00:47:56,110 --> 00:47:59,020
不,这没有原由？
No. For what purpose?

624
00:47:59,720 --> 00:48:02,620
袭击船只是有原因的
The boat was taken for a purpose.

625
00:48:03,160 --> 00:48:06,120
当他们到达目的后...
And when that purpose was accomplished...

626
00:48:06,290 --> 00:48:08,590
...就弃船了
...the boat was abandoned.

627
00:48:09,730 --> 00:48:11,420
幸好我们及时发现
We're lucky we found it this fast.

628
00:48:11,600 --> 00:48:15,730
- 船上储备的弹药呢？ - 用完了或是被偷了
- What about the reserve ammunition?   - Expended or perhaps stolen.

629
00:48:15,900 --> 00:48:18,460
我们认为可能是当地抵抗组织干的
We thought perhaps the local Resistance.

630
00:48:25,840 --> 00:48:29,800
当地抵抗组织可不会抽“幸运”牌香烟
The local Resistance doesn't smoke Lucky Strikes.

631
00:48:32,550 --> 00:48:34,920
- 少校？ - 请进
- Major?   - Come in.

632
00:48:37,560 --> 00:48:38,780
抱歉打搅你了...
I'm sorry to disturb you...

633
00:48:38,960 --> 00:48:42,650
...不过我要跟几个今天进城的人碰头
...but I'm going to see some of the men who went into the city today.

634
00:48:42,830 --> 00:48:44,090
好的
All right.

635
00:48:44,260 --> 00:48:46,390
你去圣米歇尔打探情况
You go to St. Michel, find out what's happening.

636
00:48:46,570 --> 00:48:48,930
- 然后我告知我的人  - 好的
- In the meantime, I'll brief my men.   - Good.

637
00:48:49,100 --> 00:48:50,360
玛丽...
Marie...

638
00:48:50,540 --> 00:48:53,470
...你离开法国和亲人会不会很痛苦？
...is it gonna be difficult to leave France and your family?

639
00:48:53,640 --> 00:48:55,770
我很小的时候母亲就死了...
My mother died when I was a child...

640
00:48:55,940 --> 00:48:58,930
...我的兄弟死在战争爆发的第一天
...and my brother was killed in the first days of the war.

641
00:49:00,850 --> 00:49:03,110
现在我父亲也走了...
Now that my father is gone...

642
00:49:03,280 --> 00:49:05,680
...我唯一的亲人就是抵抗组织
...the only family I have is the Resistance.

643
00:49:05,850 --> 00:49:07,650
我很抱歉
I'm sorry.

644
00:49:07,820 --> 00:49:10,980
你知道战争是很残酷的吧,玛丽？
You really must know what war is all about, right, Marie?

645
00:49:37,280 --> 00:49:38,980
真漂亮
Beautiful.

646
00:49:39,590 --> 00:49:41,180
是的,不过你要小心点
Yes, but take a good look.

647
00:49:41,350 --> 00:49:43,180
别忘了你现在是个修道士,好吧？
Now, remember, you're a monk, okay?

648
00:49:43,360 --> 00:49:46,420
你已经发誓要虔诚、平和
You've taken vows of piety and nonviolence.

649
00:49:46,990 --> 00:49:49,760
你要装好,否则我们就完了
You fake it good, or we're dead.

650
00:50:04,910 --> 00:50:07,140
早上好,神父
Morning, holy Fathers.

651
00:50:10,120 --> 00:50:14,640
- 你们来自尼姆？ - 是,我们修道会的新家
- I see you've come from Nimes.   - Yes, the new home of our order.

652
00:50:14,820 --> 00:50:17,450
但我们希望能在这里做祷告
But we have a great desire to pray here, if we may.

653
00:50:17,620 --> 00:50:20,250
当然,我们不会与上帝为敌
Oh, of course,are we the enemies of God?

654
00:50:21,990 --> 00:50:23,690
你们从南希来？
Did you come by Nancy?

655
00:50:23,860 --> 00:50:25,800
不是,我们从沙龙来
No, by way of Chalon.

656
00:50:25,960 --> 00:50:29,130
那样不但快,而且沿途的景色也更美
It's much faster, and the scenery is much more pleasant.

657
00:50:30,970 --> 00:50:32,660
我也这样觉得
My impression exactly.

658
00:50:37,910 --> 00:50:40,140
谢谢你们,神父
Thank you, holy Father.

659
00:51:09,310 --> 00:51:11,210
你刚才表现不错
You did a good job with the sentry.

660
00:51:11,380 --> 00:51:13,040
谢谢。我以前当过祭童
Thank you. I was an altar boy.

661
00:51:13,210 --> 00:51:15,700
我早该猜到
Of course. I should have guessed.

662
00:51:30,430 --> 00:51:32,590
那个项目主管不会不来了吧？
Suppose your project director doesn't show up?

663
00:51:32,760 --> 00:51:34,100
不会,他会来的
No, he'll be here.

664
00:51:34,270 --> 00:51:36,100
听着,我们离开时...
Look, when we leave...

665
00:51:36,270 --> 00:51:38,670
...你告诉纳粹中士我们想再来
...you tell the SS sergeant we want to return again.

666
00:51:38,840 --> 00:51:40,500
就在今晚
Tonight.

667
00:51:41,110 --> 00:51:42,770
我就对他说要进行晚间祷告
Could be evening prayer.

668
00:51:42,940 --> 00:51:44,410
这对修道士非常重要
Very important for monks.

669
00:51:44,580 --> 00:51:46,310
很好
Perfect.

670
00:51:58,760 --> 00:52:01,020
下午好,修士们
Good afternoon, brothers.

671
00:52:01,190 --> 00:52:03,060
我猜你们一定是走了很远的路吧？
I think you have come a very long way.

672
00:52:03,230 --> 00:52:05,090
为了寻找上帝
In search of God.

673
00:52:05,260 --> 00:52:07,820
我们都得经历这样的旅程
That's a journey we all must make.

674
00:52:08,000 --> 00:52:10,800
弗莱蒙先生,我们今晚就把你们救出去
Monsieur Flamands, we're taking you out of here tonight.

675
00:52:10,970 --> 00:52:12,440
好极了
Good.

676
00:52:12,600 --> 00:52:14,270
我开始整理笔记...
I'll start collecting my notes...

677
00:52:14,440 --> 00:52:16,700
...并告知小组其他成员
...and advising the other members of my group.

678
00:52:16,880 --> 00:52:20,040
当然,副主管皮埃尔.克劳德除外
Except, of course, for my assistant director, Pierre Claudel.

679
00:52:20,450 --> 00:52:22,610
- 为何不告诉他？ - 他是个法国纳粹
- And why not him?   - He's a French Nazi.

680
00:52:22,780 --> 00:52:24,650
是维希人和“火十字团”的混血儿
Part of Vichy, part of the Croix de Feu.

681
00:52:24,980 --> 00:52:27,180
也许是他害死了当地的抵抗运动领袖...
He may have caused the death of Paul Verlaine...

682
00:52:27,350 --> 00:52:28,880
...保罗.维兰尼
...the local Resistance leader.

683
00:52:29,120 --> 00:52:30,350
少校
Major.

684
00:52:30,820 --> 00:52:33,590
- 那人可能会泄露我们的行动  - 他还蒙在鼓里
- That man could blow this thing open.   - He doesn't know.

685
00:52:33,760 --> 00:52:36,420
如果他知道的话早就检举我们了
If he knew more, he would have denounced us already.

686
00:52:36,830 --> 00:52:38,060
计划如下...
The plan.

687
00:52:38,230 --> 00:52:39,750
我们午夜后过来
We come here after midnight.

688
00:52:39,930 --> 00:52:41,660
炸毁目标...
We blow up our target...

689
00:52:41,830 --> 00:52:43,700
...20分钟内把你们救出去
...and get you out in less than 20 minutes.

690
00:52:43,870 --> 00:52:45,100
应该可行
That's possible.

691
00:52:45,270 --> 00:52:48,100
但你们要在炸毁目标前把我们救出修道院
But you must get us out of the monastery before you blow it up.

692
00:52:48,270 --> 00:52:50,470
- 我们会的  - 你们有足够的时间...
- We'll do that.   - You'll have plenty of time...

693
00:52:51,040 --> 00:52:54,070
...跟你们得妻子告别
...to make sure your wives are safe and kiss them goodbye.

694
00:52:54,750 --> 00:52:56,940
- 你在说什么？ - 弗莱蒙先生
- What are you talking about?   - Monsieur Flamands.

695
00:52:57,120 --> 00:52:59,810
我们来的时候不知道你们家人也在
We didn't know about your families when we landed.

696
00:52:59,990 --> 00:53:02,580
这是军事撤退
This is a military evacuation.

697
00:53:02,750 --> 00:53:05,450
我们现在的问题是飞机位置不够
We've got a problem. We just don't have any room.

698
00:53:05,620 --> 00:53:07,350
那怎么行
Then it's impossible.

699
00:53:07,530 --> 00:53:10,290
难道你不知道纳粹之所以把我妻子...
Don't you realize what would happen to my wife...

700
00:53:10,460 --> 00:53:11,690
...和其他人扣为人质...
...and other hostages...

701
00:53:11,860 --> 00:53:14,230
...就是想以此来要挟我们？
...the Nazis could think of to threaten us with?

702
00:53:14,400 --> 00:53:16,330
否则我们怎么会为他们做事？
Why else do you think we worked for them?

703
00:53:16,500 --> 00:53:19,660
或许是因为你对纯科学研究感兴趣
Perhaps because of your interest in pure science.

704
00:53:24,640 --> 00:53:27,110
我家人会挂念我的
I will be missed at my desk.

705
00:53:28,110 --> 00:53:32,740
我再强调一次,如果不带上我妻子,我哪儿也不去
Make no mistake, I'm going nowhere without my wife.

706
00:53:33,620 --> 00:53:35,780
我们也会准备好的
We will be ready in any case.

707
00:53:44,700 --> 00:53:45,690
皮埃尔
Pierre.

708
00:53:46,100 --> 00:53:49,430
没想到你也信奉上帝,乔治
I had no idea there was a religious streak in you, George.

709
00:53:53,440 --> 00:53:55,300
克雷格上校要跟你通话
Colonel Krieger is on the phone.

710
00:53:56,470 --> 00:53:57,940
谢谢
Thank you.

711
00:54:26,740 --> 00:54:27,970
好了
All right.

712
00:54:28,140 --> 00:54:30,870
现在,抵抗组织会开两辆车到修道院后门
Now the Resistance will have two trucks in back of the abbey.

713
00:54:31,080 --> 00:54:34,340
要不要带他们的家眷去观光？
How about a tour bus and a guide for these husbands and wives?

714
00:54:34,510 --> 00:54:36,810
少校,把他们都救出来太疯狂了
Major, it is crazy to go bring them out.

715
00:54:36,980 --> 00:54:38,540
要是飞机无法起飞怎么办？
Suppose the plane won't take off?

716
00:54:38,750 --> 00:54:40,120
放心,肯定能飞起来的
Oh, it will take off.

717
00:54:40,290 --> 00:54:42,050
而且,飞机也不够大
Besides, the flight's not that long.

718
00:54:42,220 --> 00:54:45,590
必要情况下,我们可以丢弃一些备用燃料
And if we have to, we'll jettison some of the reserve fuel.

719
00:54:45,760 --> 00:54:49,420
少校,你说过此地区领空的德机占全法国德机的一半
Major,You said half the German air force in France is in this area.

720
00:54:49,590 --> 00:54:51,530
你能带我们这些人一起逃出去吗？
You gonna outrun them with these people?

721
00:54:51,700 --> 00:54:53,820
是的,必要时只能如此。你想想...
Yes, if I have to. Look...

722
00:54:54,000 --> 00:54:56,400
...这些科学家不肯抛弃他们的妻子...
...the scientists won't leave without their wives...

723
00:54:56,570 --> 00:54:58,540
...而我的任务就是带他们逃离这里
...and it's my job to get them out of here.

724
00:54:58,700 --> 00:55:00,170
不,少校
No, major.

725
00:55:01,470 --> 00:55:04,310
你的任务是炸毁修道院...
Your job is to knock out that monastery...

726
00:55:04,480 --> 00:55:06,810
...让那些科学家不再为德军..
...and to keep scientists from showing the Germans...

727
00:55:06,980 --> 00:55:09,070
...制造更多的毒气
...to make more effective poison gas.

728
00:55:09,250 --> 00:55:11,010
你什么意思？
What the hell are you talking about?

729
00:55:11,180 --> 00:55:13,010
让他们自己选择,少校
Give them a choice, major.

730
00:55:13,180 --> 00:55:15,050
就像军队让我们选择一样
The same choice the Army gave us.

731
00:55:15,220 --> 00:55:17,280
要么走,要么留
You go or you stay.

732
00:55:17,760 --> 00:55:19,950
如果这些人不识趣,我们就干掉他们
Now if these people don't buy it, we'll stop them.

733
00:55:20,130 --> 00:55:22,250
让他们不光没法再制造毒气...
Not only from making more gas...

734
00:55:22,430 --> 00:55:24,790
...也没法再在其他地方建立实验室...
...but also from setting up another laboratory...

735
00:55:24,960 --> 00:55:27,520
...代替我们炸掉的这个
...to replace the one that we're about to blow up.

736
00:55:33,370 --> 00:55:34,930
你这是想把他们都杀了？
Are you talking about murdering them？

737
00:55:35,440 --> 00:55:38,070
现在是战争时期,少校
We are in a war, major.

738
00:55:38,980 --> 00:55:40,970
他们有选择的机会
They have a choice.

739
00:55:42,150 --> 00:55:44,210
你想把我们这些人给抛下吗？
You wanna leave it up to these boys here?

740
00:55:44,380 --> 00:55:47,820
- 要投票决定吗？ - 也许方提纳说得对,少校
- To vote on this?   - Maybe Fontenac's right, major.

741
00:55:47,990 --> 00:55:50,960
让他们选择吧。纳粹需要的只是他们的智慧
Let them have a choice. They're the brains the Nazis need.

742
00:55:51,420 --> 00:55:53,650
不,他说的不对！
No, he's wrong!

743
00:55:53,830 --> 00:55:55,620
我不会把他们抛弃在那里
And I'm not leaving here without them.

744
00:56:01,270 --> 00:56:04,600
- 玛丽,怎么了？ - 得有人去开卡车
- Yes, Marie, what is it?   - Someone men must go get the trucks.

745
00:56:04,770 --> 00:56:06,930
其他人必须回家
Others must get back to their families.

746
00:56:07,110 --> 00:56:09,900
纳粹党卫军在圣米歇尔挨家挨户搜查
The SS is conducting house-to-house searches in St. Michel.

747
00:56:10,080 --> 00:56:12,910
这样看,他们肯定已经找到了巡逻船
Well, the Germans must have discovered the patrol boat.

748
00:56:13,080 --> 00:56:14,600
或者发现船失踪了
Or they know it's missing.

749
00:56:14,780 --> 00:56:16,870
不过德军的其他行动可能对我们有利
But they have other duties which may help us.

750
00:56:17,050 --> 00:56:20,480
今晚本地区的新指挥官会到来
The new army general has arrived to command the region.

751
00:56:20,650 --> 00:56:23,180
他们会在别墅为他举行欢迎仪式
There is a reception tonight for him at the villa.

752
00:56:23,360 --> 00:56:25,590
德军高级将领都会参加吧？
And the reception will tie up the top brass, huh?

753
00:56:27,190 --> 00:56:29,320
很好,终于找到突破口了
All right. We finally got a break.

754
00:56:29,490 --> 00:56:31,190
如果他们款待将军的话...
If they're entertaining the general...

755
00:56:31,360 --> 00:56:34,760
...修道院今晚的防卫也许会比较松懈
...maybe security won't be as tough at the abbey tonight. Maybe.

756
00:56:52,580 --> 00:56:55,110
克劳德已经来了一会了
Claudel was here a moment ago.

757
00:56:55,290 --> 00:56:58,080
- 他说我们该穿好衣服了  - 好的
- He says we have to get dressed.   - That's right.

758
00:56:58,260 --> 00:57:00,690
新指挥官今晚想见我们
The new German commandant wants to see us tonight.

759
00:57:00,860 --> 00:57:02,380
我们都要参加他的晚宴
We are to be his guests at dinner.

760
00:57:02,560 --> 00:57:04,690
你不是说美军会救我们出去
You said the Americans are coming to take us out.

761
00:57:04,860 --> 00:57:08,630
我知道,但我联系不上行动负责人
I know, but I can't contact the American officer leading the attack.

762
00:57:08,800 --> 00:57:11,930
我不知道他会有怎样的反应
I don't know what his reaction would be if I did.

763
00:57:12,100 --> 00:57:14,200
尤其是我全盘托出的话
Especially if I told him everything.

764
00:57:14,370 --> 00:57:16,970
你没告诉他我们的事？
Did you tell him about us?

765
00:57:17,140 --> 00:57:19,610
他们知道我们的妻子也在这里
He knows that there are wives.

766
00:57:19,780 --> 00:57:21,610
其他就一无所知
He doesn't know more than that.

767
00:57:21,780 --> 00:57:24,370
那你和我必须跟克劳德走
Then you and I must go with Claudel.

768
00:57:25,320 --> 00:57:26,720
那个可恶的纳粹
That damn Nazi.

769
00:57:28,820 --> 00:57:32,120
- 亲一下,爸爸  - 来吧,儿子
- A kiss, Papa.   - But of course, my son.

770
00:57:33,490 --> 00:57:35,080
妈妈说你们要出去
Mother says you're going out.

771
00:57:35,260 --> 00:57:38,490
是的,我们要去圣米歇尔几个小时
Yes, we have to go into St. Michel for a few hours.

772
00:57:38,660 --> 00:57:40,260
就你妈和我去,对不起
Just your mother and I. Sorry.

773
00:57:40,430 --> 00:57:42,370
你要我们今晚准备好的
You said we had to be ready tonight.

774
00:57:42,530 --> 00:57:44,060
是的,孩子
That's right, my son.

775
00:57:44,240 --> 00:57:46,930
我们要跟你分开一会儿
And you may have to go somewhere without us for a while.

776
00:57:47,110 --> 00:57:49,070
- 就一会儿  - 你是说像去上学一样
- Just a while.   - You mean like the school?

777
00:57:49,240 --> 00:57:50,940
是的,像去上学
Yes, like the school.

778
00:57:51,110 --> 00:57:54,340
无论发生什么事,你都要跟你的朋友和杜弗伦博士在一起
No matter what happens, you stay with your friends and Dr. Dufresne.

779
00:57:54,550 --> 00:57:57,710
- 明白了吗？ - 我们现在都是军人了？
- Is that clear?   - We're all soldiers now?

780
00:57:59,280 --> 00:58:01,650
哪有那么小的军人
So young to be a soldier.

781
00:58:08,260 --> 00:58:10,820
我的人会带你们进入修道院的地窖
My people will get you into the wine cellar of the abbey.

782
00:58:11,000 --> 00:58:12,960
我们今晚十点离开。祝好运,少校
We leave at 10 tonight. Good luck, major.

783
00:58:13,130 --> 00:58:16,460
好的,我待会布置行动计划,马丁内兹
All right, I'll lay out that plan later. Martinez.

784
00:58:17,970 --> 00:58:21,630
我不小心听到你们谈话了
I couldn't help overhearing some of the conversation.

785
00:58:21,810 --> 00:58:23,600
如果带上我会麻烦的话...
If there is a problem in taking me...

786
00:58:23,780 --> 00:58:26,940
...我可以往南逃到西班牙
...I can head south, and then try for Spain.

787
00:58:27,110 --> 00:58:29,080
玛丽,我会带你离开的
Marie, I'll get you out of here.

788
00:58:36,050 --> 00:58:37,280
你想怎样,少校？
What do you want, major?

789
00:58:37,460 --> 00:58:38,680
你想试探我们..
You trying to find out...

790
00:58:38,860 --> 00:58:41,290
...看关键时刻谁会站在你那边？
...who's on your side if there's a showdown?

791
00:58:41,460 --> 00:58:43,650
我可以告诉你,不会有人站在你那边
I can tell you. No one.

792
00:58:45,130 --> 00:58:48,430
- 你呢,史坦？ - 我是来杀德国佬的
- What about you, Stern?   - I came here to kill Germans.

793
00:58:48,700 --> 00:58:52,000
好了,我查过你的背景...
Okay. You know, I did a little checking into your record...

794
00:58:52,170 --> 00:58:55,200
- 你干嘛多管闲事,少校  - ...在你受训的时候
- You should mind your own business,Major.   - ... while you were training.

795
00:58:55,370 --> 00:58:56,840
你抢的三间银行都是...
Those three banks you robbed...

796
00:58:57,010 --> 00:58:59,770
...泛德银行的支行
...all branches of Trans-German Nord.

797
00:58:59,940 --> 00:59:03,540
那是纽约最大的德国银行
The largest German-owned trading bank in New York.

798
00:59:03,720 --> 00:59:05,440
也许我并不知道
Maybe I didn't know that.

799
00:59:05,620 --> 00:59:07,110
或许吧
Maybe not.

800
00:59:07,290 --> 00:59:09,910
还有你走私的枪支
Or those guns you were arrested for smuggling.

801
00:59:10,090 --> 00:59:11,420
我军都还没装备...
All wound up in countries...

802
00:59:11,590 --> 00:59:14,490
...那些枪就留到抗德和抗日的...
...fighting against the Germans and the Japanese...

803
00:59:14,660 --> 00:59:16,390
...国家去了
...even before we got into it.

804
00:59:16,560 --> 00:59:18,390
- 我告诉过你...  - 你没有
- I told you....   - No.

805
00:59:18,560 --> 00:59:22,230
你一个字都没跟我说过,不过我告诉你
You haven't told me a damn thing, but I'm telling you.

806
00:59:22,400 --> 00:59:23,990
你心里想的那些...
Whatever you got up there...

807
00:59:24,170 --> 00:59:25,500
...会把你给毁了的
...it's tearing you apart.

808
00:59:25,670 --> 00:59:27,040
那又有什么区别？
What difference does it make?

809
00:59:27,210 --> 00:59:30,330
再过几小时我们全都会送命
We're all going to be dead in a few hours.

810
00:59:35,380 --> 00:59:37,440
史坦不是我的真名
Stern isn't my real name.

811
00:59:37,620 --> 00:59:39,340
是带我离开德国的...
It's the name of the family...

812
00:59:39,520 --> 00:59:41,820
...那家人的姓
...I was smuggled out of Germany to live with.

813
00:59:43,090 --> 00:59:44,650
你的真名很重要吗？
Well, is your real name important?

814
00:59:45,560 --> 00:59:47,020
不重要
No.

815
00:59:47,190 --> 00:59:51,150
我家族人大多都死了
Most of the people who had it are probably already dead.

816
00:59:51,530 --> 00:59:54,020
本来我们家族人丁兴旺,少校
There were literally dozens of us, major.

817
00:59:54,200 --> 00:59:55,690
现在或许就剩我一个了
Maybe I'm the last one.

818
00:59:55,870 --> 00:59:58,800
所以,那六个为纳粹做事的科学家的死活...
So those six scientists working for the Nazis...

819
00:59:58,970 --> 01:00:01,500
...你根本就不在乎
...whether they live or die, you don't give a damn.

820
01:00:02,910 --> 01:00:05,270
你说得没错,少校
You got it, major.

821
01:00:08,250 --> 01:00:09,940
我很遗憾
I'm sorry.

822
01:00:10,110 --> 01:00:11,840
我也是
So am I.

823
01:00:35,210 --> 01:00:36,570
卡尔.霍夫勒中尉
Lieutenant Karl Hoeffler.

824
01:00:36,740 --> 01:00:38,610
他负责指挥巡逻船,上校
He commanded the patrol boat, colonel.

825
01:00:38,780 --> 01:00:40,710
有没找到其他水手的尸体？
Any other sailors' bodies recovered yet?

826
01:00:40,880 --> 01:00:43,810
没有。但我们知道攻击的发生地点...
No,Sir。but we know the area where the attack must have taken place...

827
01:00:43,980 --> 01:00:46,750
...我们会继续搜寻的
...and we will continue searching.

828
01:00:47,450 --> 01:00:49,720
他是为元首捐躯的
He died for his Fuhrer.

829
01:00:50,960 --> 01:00:54,220
我们关押了多少抵抗组织的成员？
How many Resistance members do we have in detention?

830
01:00:54,390 --> 01:00:55,620
6个,上校
Six, colonel.

831
01:00:55,790 --> 01:00:57,590
把他们都绞死
Hang them.

832
01:00:58,000 --> 01:01:00,660
这是帝国警察领袖希姆莱的命令
Orders of Reichsleiter Himmler.

833
01:01:02,630 --> 01:01:04,530
发布一个报复的告示
Post a notice of retaliation.

834
01:01:04,700 --> 01:01:06,830
告诉他们,这些人...
State that they are being executed in reprisal...

835
01:01:07,010 --> 01:01:08,730
...要为死去的德国水手偿命
...for the murder of German sailors.

836
01:01:09,040 --> 01:01:13,740
告诉大家,如果有人揭发真凶,我就会赦免...
State that I may spare the six if those who actually committed the murders...

837
01:01:13,910 --> 01:01:15,640
...这六个人
...are identified.

838
01:01:19,180 --> 01:01:22,450
玛丽和游击队员今晚跟我们在修道院北边碰头
Marie and the partisans will meet us at the north end of the monastery.

839
01:01:22,620 --> 01:01:25,090
马丁内兹,你跟史坦取出毒气罐...
Martinez, you and Stern take out the canisters. Holt...

840
01:01:25,260 --> 01:01:27,550
...霍特,你解决岗哨的士兵...
...you wipe out the gun tower, then get inside...

841
01:01:27,730 --> 01:01:29,450
...溜进去炸掉它
...and blow the place to hell.

842
01:01:29,630 --> 01:01:31,790
应该没问题
Maybe I can do this one.

843
01:01:31,960 --> 01:01:34,020
巴勒斯和查科...
Ballews and Chacon will go and support you...

844
01:01:34,200 --> 01:01:35,760
...从阳台上方协助你
...from the upper balconies.

845
01:01:35,930 --> 01:01:39,890
你们有2分钟时间去消灭修道院的德军
You got 20 minutes to secure the monastery.

846
01:02:33,520 --> 01:02:36,250
嗨,老波,方提纳在哪里？
Hey, Pops. Where's Fontenac?

847
01:02:36,430 --> 01:02:38,160
他说他要去当守卫
He said he was gonna pull guard duty.

848
01:02:38,330 --> 01:02:41,960
那个混蛋骗子,快！
That lying bastard. Come on!

849
01:02:52,780 --> 01:02:56,510
动一下我就把你的喉咙割了
You move and I'll cut your throat out.

850
01:02:57,120 --> 01:02:58,810
去叫少校
Get the major.

851
01:02:59,620 --> 01:03:01,850
先让我把这个人渣解决了
After I get rid of this pig.

852
01:03:02,020 --> 01:03:03,250
不行！
No!

853
01:03:03,620 --> 01:03:05,710
你没权处置他,少校才有权
You don't make that decision. The major does.

854
01:03:07,990 --> 01:03:10,320
我待会再回来
I'll be right back.

855
01:03:14,170 --> 01:03:16,360
你真是不同凡响,莫瑞斯
Oh, you're beautiful, Maurice.

856
01:03:16,530 --> 01:03:18,870
真是上帝的杰作
You're a real work of art.

857
01:03:30,620 --> 01:03:32,410
究竟怎么回事？
What the hell happened?

858
01:03:59,440 --> 01:04:01,440
我能帮什么忙吗？
Is there anything I can do to help?

859
01:04:01,610 --> 01:04:03,240
把他们赶出去
Get them out of here.

860
01:04:03,410 --> 01:04:05,010
你不知道他们的底细,是吧？
You don't know who these men are, do you?

861
01:04:05,180 --> 01:04:07,170
我当然知道
Of course I do.

862
01:04:07,350 --> 01:04:09,750
他们是经过挑选的士兵,对吧？
They're a picked unit, right?

863
01:04:09,920 --> 01:04:11,890
精英队伍,千里迢迢...
Elite troops come all the way...

864
01:04:12,060 --> 01:04:14,490
- ...从美国来拯救法国  - 不,不是的
- ... from America to save France.   - No, no.

865
01:04:14,660 --> 01:04:17,560
我实话告诉你吧,几周前...
Suppose I told you that a few weeks ago...

866
01:04:17,730 --> 01:04:19,490
...这些人都还呆在牢里
...these men were in a military prison.

867
01:04:19,700 --> 01:04:22,930
- 大多数都是绞刑犯  - 你说什么？
- Most of them sentenced to hang.   - What are you talking about?

868
01:04:23,100 --> 01:04:24,690
这是真的,玛丽
It's true, Marie.

869
01:04:24,870 --> 01:04:28,270
他们被挑出来执行任务,并非因为他们是“精英”
These men were picked for this mission, not because they're "elite. "

870
01:04:28,440 --> 01:04:30,340
而是因为他们的死活不重要
Because they're expendable.

871
01:04:30,510 --> 01:04:33,940
不是因为他们是美军的骄傲
Not because the United States Army is proud of them, no.

872
01:04:34,110 --> 01:04:36,310
他们都是窃贼或杀人犯
They're thieves and killers.

873
01:04:36,480 --> 01:04:38,210
那你又是什么？
Then what are you?

874
01:04:38,380 --> 01:04:40,210
嗯...
Well...

875
01:04:40,380 --> 01:04:42,410
...我是负责挑选...
...I'm the officer who picks them...

876
01:04:42,590 --> 01:04:44,110
...训练...
...trains them...

877
01:04:44,290 --> 01:04:47,780
...带他们执行任务的军官...
...leads them into action, and more often than not...

878
01:04:47,960 --> 01:04:49,790
...通常他们都无法生还
...most of them are killed doing the job.

879
01:04:50,330 --> 01:04:51,820
玛丽
Marie.

880
01:04:52,630 --> 01:04:55,360
我不能处决方提纳,即使我也很想
I can't kill Fontenac now even if I wanted to.

881
01:04:55,530 --> 01:04:57,470
我需要带他去修道院
I need him to get back into the monastery.

882
01:04:57,640 --> 01:04:59,730
展开行动
To launch the attack.

883
01:05:00,810 --> 01:05:03,370
但对于这次任务而言,玛丽...
But for this mission, Marie...

884
01:05:03,540 --> 01:05:05,480
...你更重要
...you're even more important.

885
01:05:08,180 --> 01:05:10,670
你准备好了就叫我
Call me when you're ready.

886
01:05:18,420 --> 01:05:20,790
任务结束后...
When it's over...

887
01:05:20,960 --> 01:05:24,290
...我要亲手杀了方提纳
...I kill Fontenac myself.

888
01:07:05,260 --> 01:07:08,250
爸爸妈妈怎么还没回来？
Shouldn't my father and mother be back now?

889
01:07:08,430 --> 01:07:10,660
你得耐心点,费德里克
You must be patient, Fredric.

890
01:07:10,840 --> 01:07:13,000
冷静一点
Try to be calm.

891
01:08:00,920 --> 01:08:03,610
冲进去后,我来负责通讯室
When we get inside, I'll take care of the Communications Room.

892
01:08:03,790 --> 01:08:05,450
你们去到建筑后面...
You go to the rear of the building...

893
01:08:05,620 --> 01:08:08,850
...确保马丁内兹和其他人把炸药带进来
...and make sure that Martinez and the others get in with the explosives.

894
01:08:09,030 --> 01:08:11,190
都听你的,少校
Whatever you say, major.

895
01:08:52,770 --> 01:08:54,070
现在很晚了,神父
It's late, Fathers.

896
01:08:54,240 --> 01:08:57,070
还不算太晚,中士
It is not too late, I hope, sergeant.

897
01:08:57,240 --> 01:08:59,770
上帝应该还没入睡
I'm sure God is still awake.

898
01:09:08,590 --> 01:09:09,990
快上,史坦
Go, Stern.

899
01:10:03,670 --> 01:10:06,010
英国的飞机90分钟后会到
The plane from England will touch down in 90 minutes.

900
01:10:06,180 --> 01:10:08,480
我们午夜就能回去了吧？
I guess we'll be on our way home by midnight, right?

901
01:10:08,650 --> 01:10:10,310
对
You got it.

902
01:10:10,480 --> 01:10:12,880
我很好奇,一个避世索居的修道士...
I was curious as to how a monk...

903
01:10:13,050 --> 01:10:17,710
...为何竟会认得纳粹中士的徽章
...living in isolation recognizes the insignia of an SS sergeant.

904
01:12:00,320 --> 01:12:03,990
你要溜出去散步吗,莫瑞斯？
Thinking of taking a little stroll, Maurice?

905
01:12:05,330 --> 01:12:07,920
我可以把你弄到西班牙去
I can get us into Spain.

906
01:12:08,270 --> 01:12:09,490
要一起去吗？
Want to come along?

907
01:12:10,200 --> 01:12:13,730
敢踏出大门一步我就打爆你的头
Go through that door and I'll blow you to hell.

908
01:12:21,250 --> 01:12:22,840
好吧,我们走
All right, come on.

909
01:13:41,530 --> 01:13:44,120
凯利,我们进去吧
Come on, Kelly, let's get inside.

910
01:15:10,710 --> 01:15:12,050
不
No!

911
01:16:19,420 --> 01:16:20,910
老波？
Pops?

912
01:16:21,080 --> 01:16:23,250
瑞典小子,去帮老波
Swede, help Pops.

913
01:16:26,460 --> 01:16:27,510
怎么了？
What happened?

914
01:16:27,690 --> 01:16:30,390
化学物质触发了燃烧弹,它们爆炸了
The chemicals must've affected the incendiaries. They exploded.

915
01:16:30,560 --> 01:16:33,030
- 科学家的妻子们呢？ - 在地窖的另一头
- Where are the wives?   - On the other side of the cellars.

916
01:16:33,200 --> 01:16:36,760
马丁内兹,你到楼上去把守
Martinez, you go upstairs and make sure nothing's moving.

917
01:16:36,930 --> 01:16:39,230
凯利,史坦,你们跟我走
Kelly, Stern. You come with me.

918
01:17:03,590 --> 01:17:06,320
- 走吧  - 什么...？这些孩子是谁的？
- Let's go.   - What...? Who are these children?

919
01:17:06,500 --> 01:17:09,090
这礼拜学校休学,他们就过来这里了
They were brought here when their schools closed this week.

920
01:17:09,270 --> 01:17:12,260
说是额外关照,但实质是把他们当做人质
Supposedly as a bonus, but of course they are hostages.

921
01:17:12,440 --> 01:17:15,300
德军马上就要来了
The whole damn German army will be here in a minute.

922
01:17:15,470 --> 01:17:17,410
我们怎么带上他们？
What are we gonna do with them?

923
01:17:27,050 --> 01:17:28,680
走吧
Let's go.

924
01:18:25,940 --> 01:18:29,340
新来的德军指挥官邀请了弗莱蒙夫妇去他别墅了
The new German commander invited Flamands and his wife to his villa.

925
01:18:29,510 --> 01:18:31,040
不能等弗莱蒙夫妇了
We have to leave without Flamands.

926
01:18:31,210 --> 01:18:35,410
不行,他是最了解Z-17的人
You can't. He knows more about Z-17 than the rest of us put together.

927
01:18:35,590 --> 01:18:37,280
如果纳粹抓住他...
If the Nazis have him...

928
01:18:37,450 --> 01:18:40,820
...他们可以在数周内重建你们摧毁的实验室
...they can put back everything you have destroyed in a matter of weeks.

929
01:18:40,990 --> 01:18:43,290
我们没法把所有人都带走,少校
We can't get the whole group out of here, major.

930
01:18:43,460 --> 01:18:45,520
我们把科学家带走,其他都留下
Let's take the scientists and leave the others.

931
01:18:45,700 --> 01:18:50,190
你疯了吗？他们今晚处决了六个圣米歇尔的人质...
Are you crazy? They just executed six hostages in St. Michel tonight...

932
01:18:50,370 --> 01:18:53,600
...就是因为你们杀死了那些水手,而抵抗组织里...
...because you killed those sailors and no one in the whole Resistance...

933
01:18:53,770 --> 01:18:55,290
...有没人肯举报你们
...would give you up to the Nazis.

934
01:18:55,470 --> 01:18:57,460
你怎么不告诉我他们劫持了人质？
Why didn't you tell me they'd taken hostages?

935
01:18:57,640 --> 01:18:59,610
那有什么区别？
What could it change?

936
01:18:59,780 --> 01:19:02,640
如果我们抛下他们的妻子和孩子...
But the wives and children will go to the concentration camps...

937
01:19:02,810 --> 01:19:04,710
- ...他们都会被关进集中营  - 你说得对
- ... if we leave them behind.   - You're right.

938
01:19:05,720 --> 01:19:07,910
我们要把他们都带走
We're getting them all out.

939
01:19:08,090 --> 01:19:10,750
把他们带上卡车,一起去乘飞机
Now get these people to the trucks and onto the plane.

940
01:19:10,920 --> 01:19:12,890
史坦,你跟我一起去别墅
Stern, you and I are going to the villa.

941
01:19:13,060 --> 01:19:15,990
如果我们一小时内没有回来就起飞
If we're not back within the hour, take off.

942
01:19:17,760 --> 01:19:19,700
这是命令
Now, that's an order.

943
01:20:29,230 --> 01:20:31,260
这身制服倒是不错
That uniform's not a bad fit.

944
01:20:31,440 --> 01:20:35,000
我用铁十字遮住了弹孔
Well, I used the Iron Cross to cover one of the bullet holes.

945
01:20:59,030 --> 01:21:01,460
第四排,左边第三个
Fourth row, third from the left.

946
01:21:01,630 --> 01:21:04,330
给他几分钟改时间,带他离开
Give him a couple of minutes, get him out of here.

947
01:21:04,500 --> 01:21:06,230
明白
You got it.

948
01:21:30,690 --> 01:21:33,630
- 怎么回事？ - 少校,党卫军刚才报告说...
- Yes, what is it?   - Colonel, Sicherheitsdienst just...

949
01:21:33,800 --> 01:21:36,770
...1分钟前发现一架菲斯勒168型战机...
...passed on information that a Fieseler 168 was spotted over...

950
01:21:36,930 --> 01:21:39,770
...刚飞过他们的空域并准备降落
...Charlene-Sur-Mer about 10 minutes ago and preparing to land.

951
01:21:39,940 --> 01:21:41,460
反间谍部门告诉我们...
Counterintelligence informs us...

952
01:21:41,640 --> 01:21:44,330
...现在那个区域并无合法飞机
...there are no authorized flights in that area at this time.

953
01:21:44,510 --> 01:21:47,070
你知道坐标吗？
Do you know the coordinates?

954
01:21:47,480 --> 01:21:49,880
- 在地图上标出来  - 他看见两辆卡车...
- Mark them on the map.   - He saw two trucks leave...

955
01:21:50,050 --> 01:21:53,350
...15分钟前开往苏瓦松路,上校
...and take the Soissons Road less than 15 minutes ago, colonel.

956
01:21:53,520 --> 01:21:56,780
好的,地图给我
All right, give me the map.

957
01:21:58,150 --> 01:22:02,820
他们碰头的地点大概就在这里
The rendezvous will be in this general area then.

958
01:22:03,030 --> 01:22:05,960
但他们应该还没到
But they can't have gotten there yet.

959
01:22:07,630 --> 01:22:12,360
命令在苏瓦松路上设置路障,拦住任何交通工具和行人
I want a blocking force of vehicles and men at the Soissons Road. Here.

960
01:22:12,540 --> 01:22:16,440
把他们引到北圣米歇尔的党卫军控制区
Pull them from the SS pool area in North St. Michel.

961
01:22:16,610 --> 01:22:18,040
是,长官
Yes, sir.

962
01:22:18,210 --> 01:22:21,230
把这些卡车给我拦住
I want those damn trucks stopped.

963
01:23:52,640 --> 01:23:54,800
你不知道我妻子还在这里...
Don't you realize my wife is still in there...

964
01:23:54,970 --> 01:23:57,960
...而且里面还有十几个德国军官？
...and there are more than a dozen German officers in the building?

965
01:23:58,140 --> 01:24:01,600
你的其他家人和同事都在离开法国的路上
The rest of your family and colleagues are on their way out of France.

966
01:24:01,780 --> 01:24:07,980
好啊,下午还是修道士,晚上就变成德国军官了
Well, a monk in the afternoon, and a captain in the German army at night.

967
01:24:08,280 --> 01:24:09,910
变化真大嘛
What a transformation.

968
01:24:10,090 --> 01:24:11,850
你开枪的话马上就会没命的
You shoot and you're dead in seconds.

969
01:24:12,020 --> 01:24:14,890
这跟你无关,皮埃尔,你是法国人...
This has nothing to do with you, Pierre. You are a Frenchman...

970
01:24:15,060 --> 01:24:18,430
我是法国人,我忠于马歇尔、贝当和法国政府...
Yes, I'm a Frenchman and I'm loyal to Marshal Petain and the French state...

971
01:24:18,600 --> 01:24:20,860
...而不像一些叛国贼...
...not some degenerate traitor who...

972
01:27:49,070 --> 01:27:51,270
别开枪！停火！
Hold it! Hold it!

973
01:27:54,540 --> 01:27:56,210
打开
Open it.

974
01:28:18,900 --> 01:28:20,560
打开！
Open up!

975
01:28:37,150 --> 01:28:39,640
我们去机场！
Let's get on to the airfield!

976
01:28:49,070 --> 01:28:50,460
怎么回事？
What's this coming?

977
01:29:01,810 --> 01:29:03,370
慢点
Hold it.

978
01:29:08,790 --> 01:29:10,280
究竟怎么回事？
What the hell is this?

979
01:29:10,450 --> 01:29:13,550
我是霍中士,莱特少校的手下。人差不多都到齐了
I'm Sergeant Holt for Major Wright. We have the cargo, or most of it.

980
01:29:13,720 --> 01:29:15,920
- 你们的少校呢？ - 他随后就到
- Where's your major?   - He'll be along.

981
01:29:16,090 --> 01:29:17,530
恐怕难了
Oh, I doubt it.

982
01:29:17,690 --> 01:29:21,860
- 他死在圣米歇尔了  - 他什么意思？
- He's in St. Michel. Dead.   - What's he talking about?

983
01:29:22,030 --> 01:29:24,430
莱特少校跟另一个人去圣米歇尔...
Major Wright and one of our men went to St. Michel...

984
01:29:24,600 --> 01:29:26,800
...去救项目主管和他妻子
...to bring out the project director and his wife

985
01:29:26,970 --> 01:29:28,960
他派两辆卡车到苏瓦松路...
He sent two trucks along the Soissons Road...

986
01:29:29,140 --> 01:29:32,570
...因为他猜测党卫军会发现你们在那里出现
...because he thought the SS would have a report that you'd be in the area.

987
01:29:32,740 --> 01:29:35,770
他让我们从小道沿着河口走
He sent the rest of us along a side road that ran along the estuary.

988
01:29:38,450 --> 01:29:40,310
我要等我爸爸妈妈来
I want to wait for my mother and father.

989
01:29:40,920 --> 01:29:44,610
- 到飞机里等,孩子  - 我跟孩子一起等
- Wait for them in the plane, kid.   - The kid can wait with me.

990
01:29:44,790 --> 01:29:47,720
- 没事的  - 我想还是别问...
- It's all right.   - I suppose I'm better off not asking...

991
01:29:47,890 --> 01:29:49,720
...这些女人和孩子是哪里来的
...where the women and children came from.

992
01:29:49,890 --> 01:29:52,420
- 我们该起飞了  - 少校和卡车还没到之前...
- We're already due out of here.   - We're not gonna leave...

993
01:29:52,600 --> 01:29:55,160
...我们不会离开的,凯利！
...until the major and the trucks arrive. Kelly!

994
01:29:55,330 --> 01:29:58,270
架起机关枪,严守所有道路
Set up the 30-caliber. I want you to guard all the approaches.

995
01:29:58,430 --> 01:29:59,730
他们来不了了,中士
They're not coming, sergeant.

996
01:29:59,900 --> 01:30:02,340
他么死在苏瓦松路上或者圣米歇尔了
They're dead on the Soissons Road or St. Michel.

997
01:30:02,510 --> 01:30:04,700
- 方提纳说的对  - 把枪架好,凯利！
- Fontenac's right.   - Set up that gun, Kelly!

998
01:30:04,870 --> 01:30:08,110
你会浪费掉我们活着离开的最后机会
You're blowing our last chance to get out of here alive.

999
01:30:18,860 --> 01:30:21,550
- 谢谢你们进来接我们  - 见到你真高兴,少校。我们走吧？
- Nice of you to drop in.   - Good to see you, major. Can we go?

1000
01:30:21,720 --> 01:30:24,690
不,我派了四个人开两辆卡车把纳粹引开...
No. I've sent four men and two trucks out to decoy the SS away...

1001
01:30:24,860 --> 01:30:27,060
...他们还没回来
...from the others, and they're unaccounted-for.

1002
01:30:27,260 --> 01:30:29,060
妈妈
Mama.

1003
01:30:34,740 --> 01:30:36,470
看来他们来不了了
Doesn't look like they're gonna make it.

1004
01:30:36,640 --> 01:30:39,160
- 起飞！ - 妈妈
- Move out!   - Mama.

1005
01:30:40,640 --> 01:30:42,340
费德里克！
Fredric!

1006
01:30:45,180 --> 01:30:46,550
费德里克！
Fredric!

1007
01:31:15,780 --> 01:31:19,080
我没法跟你们一起回家了,长官
I guess I won't be going home with you, sir.

1008
01:32:01,090 --> 01:32:02,350
追上他们！
After them!

1009
01:32:58,750 --> 01:33:01,180
你带领的是什么队伍,少校？
What sort of unit is it that you command, major?

1010
01:33:01,350 --> 01:33:04,790
最高机密,孩子,他们都是精英
Top secret, boys. Elite troops.

